The backend has been expanded with new **Parent** and **Admin** APIs.

Update the existing React frontend to support these new features.

## IMPORTANT

* DO NOT rebuild the frontend.
* DO NOT redesign the UI.
* DO NOT change the routing structure unless required for the new pages.
* Keep the same folder structure and architecture.
* Follow the same coding patterns already used throughout the project.
* Continue using the existing API utility/functions already present in the project.
* Every protected request should continue sending the JWT access token.

---

